{"tid":1661983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［岑子杰8月被襲案］ 15歲司機及另外兩名男子今日上庭 不准傳媒旁聽","createTime":"2019-10-18T12:59:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T14:18:47.000Z","uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c647a40cfc01cc0793f9f4d3da67cc622f2fb45d","tid":1661983,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T12:59:23.000Z","msg":"民陣召集人岑子杰8月29日在佐敦一間餐廳，被兩男以鐵通及棒球棍襲擊。當時岑子杰獲朋友保護，友人受傷送院，而疑犯上車逃去。警方早前拘捕3名男子，其中15歲少年被控串謀襲擊致造成身體傷害、及其他交通條例共4項罪名。案件今（18日）在九龍城裁判法院少年庭閉門提訊，據悉少年不准保釋，還押懲教看管至下月5日再訊。<br />\n<br />\n15歲少年被控串謀襲擊致造成身體傷害、偽造文件（違反道路條例）、駕駛時無駕駛執照、沒有第三者保險而使用車輛共4項罪名。<br />\n<br />\n法庭以保護被告利益為由，不准傳媒旁聽。據了解，控方申請押後案件，以待警方進一步調查，包括化驗涉案車輛的DNA；控方亦反對被告保釋。裁判官決定應控方申請，將案件押後至11月5日再訊，其間被告須還押懲教看管。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20191018/s00001/1571383073613/%e5%b2%91%e5%ad%90%e6%9d%b0%e8%88%87%e5%8f%8b8%e6%9c%88%e9%81%87%e8%a5%b2-15%e6%ad%b2%e5%b0%91%e5%b9%b4%e8%a2%ab%e6%8e%a7%e4%b8%b2%e8%ac%80%e8%a5%b2%e6%93%8a%e7%ad%894%e7%bd%aa%e9%a0%88%e9%82%84%e6%8a%bc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20191018%2Fs00001%2F1571383073613%2F%25e5%25b2%2591%25e5%25ad%2590%25e6%259d%25b0%25e8%2588%2587%25e5%258f%258b8%25e6%259c%2588%25e9%2581%2587%25e8%25a5%25b2-15%25e6%25ad%25b2%25e5%25b0%2591%25e5%25b9%25b4%25e8%25a2%25ab%25e6%258e%25a7%25e4%25b8%25b2%25e8%25ac%2580%25e8%25a5%25b2%25e6%2593%258a%25e7%25ad%25894%25e7%25bd%25aa%25e9%25a0%2588%25e9%2582%2584%25e6%258a%25bc&d=JQdTOMZ4NvWA5L1F4kLiz2zUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=54f5d6da\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20191018%2Fs00001%2F1571383073613%2F%25e5%25b2%2591%25e5%25ad%2590%25e6%259d%25b0%25e8%2588%2587%25e5%258f%258b8%25e6%259c%2588%25e9%2581%2587%25e8%25a5%25b2-15%25e6%25ad%25b2%25e5%25b0%2591%25e5%25b9%25b4%25e8%25a2%25ab%25e6%258e%25a7%25e4%25b8%25b2%25e8%25ac%2580%25e8%25a5%25b2%25e6%2593%258a%25e7%25ad%25894%25e7%25bd%25aa%25e9%25a0%2588%25e9%2582%2584%25e6%258a%25bc&h=f97f5210\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20191018/s00001/1571383073613/%e5%b2%91%e5%ad%90%e6%9d%b0%e8%88%87%e5%8f%8b8%e6%9c%88%e9%81%87%e8%a5%b2-15%e6%ad%b2%e5%b0%91%e5%b9%b4%e8%a2%ab%e6%8e%a7%e4%b8%b2%e8%ac%80%e8%a5%b2%e6%93%8a%e7%ad%894%e7%bd%aa%e9%a0%88%e9%82%84%e6%8a%bc</a>"},{"pid":"ad7cef39b8bf9f87861e53c9551d6c1a6d7d60e0","tid":1661983,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T13:00:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d54ebd672fdd8f87996f3b8877627620bd401fb9","tid":1661983,"uid":41292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T13:20:05.000Z","msg":"8月個單黎"},{"pid":"f8ead87ba8fe3cd7abc48b42ce4787a4033f4c41","tid":1661983,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T14:18:47.000Z","msg":"Twitter係每日必做的任務<br />\n禁兩個制都懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n快啲同我retweet哂去！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日國際新聞關香港或者抵制中國事的有：<br />\nDior (向中國道歉，承認台灣係中國）<br />\n<br />\nBlizzard(共雪禁左美國大學隊賽半年，原因係美國大學隊支持Free Hong Kong)<br />\n<br />\nDreamwork（動畫畫九段線，畫出大部分的南海係屬於中國，菲律賓嚴重抗議，荷蘭海牙仲裁已經響2016裁定九段線違反聯合國國際公約，所以Dreamwork 奶共奶到洗緊細路腦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\nnba (Lebron James 鬧Morey咩都唔知就亂tweet，大家可以提出任何人都唔應該響普世價值上助紂為虐、自我審查！）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果你響twitter大海中唔知retweet咩好<br />\ntwitter 組整左個bot<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=JQdTOMZ4NvWA5L1F4kLiz2zUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=e7599171\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你入    /task2</span></span><b